snippet.textDisplay: Listening to this beautiful Assamese song and watching the Bihu dance brought back so many childhood memories! Bihu was always a time of joy, dance, and togetherness. Now, living in Spain, I miss those vibrant celebrations even more. Thank you for this soulful performance—it truly feels like home! ❤️"

snippet.textDisplay: I was born in Assam, but I am a Bengali . Somehow I imbibed both the cultures in me. I still miss uruka, I was the only Bengali girl in my area who used to dance to “husoris” sung and danced during Bohag Bihu. Seeing, Coke Studio collaborating with the people and singers from Assam makes me proud. Thank you so much for this❤
